pymp4info - information about MP4 file in Python
-----------------------
A simple wrapper for FAAD2 library to get information about audio
track length, average bitrate and frequency. There is also tagger
for handling iTunes metadata.

FAAD2 can be found at http://www.audiocoding.com/

Building / Installation:
------------------------
The module has only been tested on Python 2.3. To build pymp4info 
you must have the FAAD2 and Python development files installed.

 $ make && make install

